reviewText: My kids love this now my grandchildren are watching

it a good set of dvds for kid's horror movies. if u want to remember the good old years or u have a younger sibling that wants to get into scary movies without the excess violence, than this dvd is good for theml.

I loved this show when I was a kid, and still do today.  I am so glad that I was able to buy them on DVD.  If it was just for the show I would give it 5 stars.  I ordered it from iNetVideo which said that i could get it new in good condition.  It took a really long time to get to me, more than 2 weeks.  Also it was in poor condition when I did get it.  The boxes were all bent and many of them had plastic broken in them.  Overall I was really unimpressed with the shipping, but it is still a great product.
